&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://regisphilibert.com/tags/hugo/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
